Quote: Bridge was the main serious(?) game at Scott Base ... A [table top] football game ... held sway for a while, till ludo or `Akkers' gripped the camp in a fever; with four boards going and the spectators and players hurling advice and abuse, ... but it was a great way of letting off steam.
Notes: Life in Antarctica
